                <h2>Welcome to Our School Management System</h2>
                <p>This comprehensive platform helps educational institutions manage all aspects of school administration, from student records to staff management and communication.</p>
                <p>Navigate through the menu above to explore different sections of our system. Each main menu item contains relevant sub-options to help you find what you need quickly.</p>
                <p>Our system is designed with educators in mind, providing intuitive tools that save time and improve efficiency in school operations.</p>
