            <!-- Timeline Section -->
            <div id="timeline" class="content-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-timeline"></i> Historical Timeline</h2>
                <p>Explore the significant milestones in our school's history that have shaped the institution we are today.</p>
                
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item left">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>1955 - Foundation</h3>
                            <p>Our school was established with 150 students and 12 faculty members in the original building that now houses our administration offices.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item right">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>1972 - First Expansion</h3>
                            <p>The science wing and library were added to accommodate growing enrollment and expanding curriculum offerings.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item left">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>1985 - Arts Program</h3>
                            <p>The performing arts center was constructed, establishing our renowned music and theater programs.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item right">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>1998 - Technology Integration</h3>
                            <p>Our school became one of the first in the state to implement comprehensive computer labs and technology curriculum.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item left">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>2010 - Green Campus Initiative</h3>
                            <p>We launched our sustainability program, installing solar panels and implementing comprehensive recycling.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item right">
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h3>2020 - Modernization Complete</h3>
                            <p>The campus modernization project was completed, featuring state-of-the-art facilities and learning spaces.</p>
                        </div>
